The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Good Morning

 Hello It's Saturday, July 23, 2005

 Debate

 Attend a debate at the XIX Annual Scientific Conference at Ramakrishna Mission Seva Pratishthan-Vivekananda Institute of Medical Sciences, 11 am.

 Listen to varied views on ?Even today, films stereotype the image of women? at an inter-collegiate debate at Bangla Akademi, 12.30 pm.

 Theatre

 Watch Cholo Potol Tuli, directed by Arindam Ganguly, at Madhusudan Mancha, 6.30 pm.

 Fair

 Visit Kitchenex 2005, an exhibition-cum-sale of kitchenware and home appliances, at Ice Skating Rink.

 Workshop

 Participate in a film appreciation workshop at Digital Academy, 46C, Jawaharlal Nehru Road, 4 pm to 7 pm.

 Exhibition

 Take a look at the exhibits at CIMA Gallery, 2 pm to 7 pm.

 Check out Bishnu De?s works at Bangiya Sahitya Parishat, 2 pm to 6 pm.

 Drop in at an exhibition at Hugli, in Garden Reach, 10.30 am-7.30 pm.




